snippet.title: Model Builder Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Don't forget to check out Model Builder:

► https://store.steampowered.com/app/1164250/Model_Builder/

Model Builder is a game about building and customizing model vehicles. Assemble, customize and display your creations - fill virtual shelves with amazing machines! Whether you’re a veteran or a novice, you are bound to have fun!

Social media channels:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/modelbuildergame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/modelbuildersim
WWW: http://www.modelbuilder.game
